Base:Descriptions.Base:Description: Thick wooden joists, clean and uneven, cross the ceiling. They support wide wooden planks, which have been plastered and whitewashed. The candles make the shadows on the ceiling dance.
The four corners of the prayer chamber.
Below your feet are white tiles of palest marble, polished to a fine sheen. Looking down you can see your own reflection:
Below your feet are white tiles of palest marble, polished to a fine sheen.
The shouthern wall of the prayer chamber stands somewhat less then eight feet high. A long border of holy scripture and symbols are painted in white and gold along the top and floor of the wall.
The western wall of the prayer chamber stands somewhat less then eight feet high. A long border of holy scripture and symbols are painted in white and gold along the top and floor of the wall.
